\end_inset

 such that for any 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{F}_{t}$
\end_inset

-measurable and bounded random variable 
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

 and any 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{E}_{\mathbb{P}}\left[Z\mid Y=y\right]=\mathbb{E}_{\mathbb{P}}\left[\eta_{t}^{y}Z\right]$
\end_inset

.
